  "body": "Changes:\r\n* To make use of the newly introduced `yyjson` flag `YYJSON_WRITE_NEWLINE_AT_END`, fastfetch now requires `yyjson` 0.9.0 or later\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n* Always add a final new-line when generating JSON output\r\n* Detect partition create time, which can be used as OS installation time (Disk)\r\n* Print time string when generating JSON result instead of UNIX epoch time number, which is more human-readable\r\n\r\nBugfixes:\r\n* Fix a memory leak\r\n* Better portable mode detection of Windows Terminal (TerminalFont, Windows)\r\n* Fix parsing of option `--packages-disabled` (Packages)\r\n* Don't use command `time` as a shell (Shell)\r\n\r\nLogos:\r\n* Add openSUSE MicroOS\r\n* Fix color of AOSC OS\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n<details><summary>SHA256SUMs</summary><br>\r\n\r\n```\r\n82578314f1c59e9c2fefa055f301f26a2d526f94aa6ccd4b57fab253b4cc6693  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.tar.gz\r\n1d64223f69f9bc99ab4d42468d5a9e476afce2b6846c61154d8c09dd663b07af  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.zip\r\n757f08a7d10ba9ecc26a44842e389d9dbbc3a728cb26eb2105509aa087291c70  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.tar.gz\r\n8f8347e7e09c41b28ebc9a96f652d544e66c1b8ae2ef3538cc026599f0794a51  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.zip\r\nd9264a5d9d143467b1a2773f1d55e0439451d4cfdc2a439a7bbedc32d6170e95  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.deb\r\nff9a4c0de429e4ae911ffdaea1af4d2d758b6fb255e09b01fb534ed9b73d0855  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.rpm\r\n29891acd6a056d8565d92b242ad280714a2cd2f03d4cbb4d524d2229024d343e  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.tar.gz\r\n39115c9009a63f0391e2610ff6a34139da450f0c90358f27c76a172d39ff5246  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.zip\r\n25c9ed94d5c8c677ee369a1f29da27667c3a8a26c884497f983acf6dc9c4c962  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.deb\r\n873d834dfa32b74e0a5f7b1b92e4df48f7cbe8f4cd94430a1739a60f3ce9c9b6  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-